quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  39,6,"O tagii on e fittaandu wooturu, refi Owa…ói e ndun, genndo mayru. O jippinani on e neemoraa…ói …óin, nooneeji jeetati. Homo taga on ka teege yumma mon en, tagu …ìaawo tagu, e ndeer ni…ìe tati. Ko On moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi mon ! Ko Ka≈ãko laamu woodani. Dewetee…óo alaa, si wonaa Allah. Ko honno perlitora…óon [e dewugol Mo]?"
  39,7,"Si on njeddii, anndon Allah, ko jondinii…óo e mon. O ja…ìantaa jiyaa…ìe makko …ìeen, ke'eferaaku. Si on njettii Mo noon, O weltanoo on …óuum.Hay gooto roondantaako go…ó…óo woo donngal mum. Refti ko ka Joomi mon, woni ruttorde mon; O yeetitoo on, fii kon ko gollatno…óon. Pellet, ko O ganndu…óo, ko woni e …ìer…óe."
  39,8,"Si loraa memii ne…ó…óo on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e makko. Refti si O okkii mo mo∆¥∆¥ere, immorde ka makko, o yejjita ko o noddatno kon ado …óuum, o wa…óana Allah kafidii…ói, fii no o majjinira (yim…ìe …ìeen) e laawol makko ngol. MaAku: "Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, see…óa. Pellet, ko a jiyaa…óo e yim…ìe Yiite …ìeen"."
  39,9,"Kaa ko on yankinotoo…óo tummbo jemma, ko o cujjoowo, darotoo…óo (naafe), hara homo La'akara, homo joortii yurmeende Joomi makko nden... Maaku: "Hara anndu…ìe …ìen fotay e …ìe nganndaa …ìen?" Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraa…ìe haqqille …ìeen."
  39,10,"Maaku: "eey mon yo jiyaa…ìe Am goo≈ã…óin…ìe, kulee Joomi mon". Hino woodani mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe (golle) …ìen e oo aduna, mbarjaari. Leydi Allah ndin ko yaajundi. Nganndee mu√±√±ii…ìe …ìeen timminirante njo…ìdi ma…ì…ìe ndin, ko aldaa e limoore."